  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张流程图，展示患者从社区到住院再到出院的完整路径，重点是暴露系统中的两个主要堵点：老年护理床位不足，以及NDIS支持匹配延迟。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "Inpatient",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。起点是Community节点，然后分两条线走GP和直接急诊？还是GP是必经之路？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GP不是必经之路。患者可以直接去急诊，也可以通过家庭医生转诊。所以Community应该分出两条线：一条到GP，一条直接到ED_Arrival。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，那GP之后也要连到ED_Arrival，形成汇聚。急诊到达之后是评估治疗环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，ED_Arrival之后是ED_Treat，也就是急诊评估和治疗。这个节点很关键，因为后面我会加一个反馈回路指向它。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加ED_Treat节点。接下来是住院决策？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ED_Treat之后是Admission，表示决定收治。然后进入Inpatient，也就是实际住院阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "住院之后是准备出院？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Ready节点表示患者临床已可出院，但这时候两个access block机制开始起作用：一个是老年护理床位排队，另一个是NDIS住宿支持不到位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这两个堵点都是风险类节点吧？需要特殊样式区分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，这两个是capacity constraint和delay/mismatch，要用risk样式。而且它们不是终结点，要画虚线反馈回路回到Inpatient，表示床位被占用形成occupancy feedback loop。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Block_Aged和Block_NDIS，并画了虚线回到Inpatient，标注occupancy feedback loop。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "很好。另外再加一条虚线从Inpatient回到ED_Treat，标注high occupancy limits flow，表示住院部满了之后急诊患者也进不来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inpatient",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "两条反馈回路都画好了。现在确认一下样式定义：cth给GP用，state给ED_Treat和Inpatient，risk给两个block节点，neutral给其他？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cth",
        "state",
