      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式已应用。检查一遍：Block_Aged的文字是\"Aged care placement (capacity constraint)\"，Block_NDIS是\"NDIS supports / accommodation (delay / mismatch)\"，对吗？",
