      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊，我说错了。GP不是独立节点，Community到ED_Arrival的边应该标注\"GP / primary care\"，同时Community还有一条直接到ED_Arrival的无标注边。",
      "elements_involved": [
